            "content": "if the result cannot be represented as a non-negative {@code long} value.",
            "assertion": "assert (Math.abs(args[0]) == Long.MIN_VALUE && Math.abs(args[1]) == Long.MIN_VALUE) || (args[0] == Long.MIN_VALUE && args[1] == 0L) || (args[0] == 0L && args[1] == Long.MIN_VALUE);",
